<node TEXT="QAbstractScrollArea&#x7c7b;" ID="ID_438892390" CREATED="1287583696009" MODIFIED="1287583727069"/>
<node TEXT="QTextCursor&#x7c7b;" ID="ID_1102705633" CREATED="1287583813787" MODIFIED="1287651827373"><richcontent TYPE="NOTE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <font face="Arial, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" size="4">A QTextCursor also has an&#160;</font><font color="rgb(103, 41, 103)" face="Arial, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="4"><a href="qtextcursor.html#anchor" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(103, 41, 103)">anchor</a></font><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Arial, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="4">() position. The text that is between the&#160;</font><font face="Arial, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="rgb(103, 41, 103)" size="4"><a href="qtextcursor.html#anchor" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(103, 41, 103)">anchor</a></font><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Arial, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="4">() and the&#160;</font><font face="Arial, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="rgb(0, 70, 173)" size="4"><a href="qtextcursor.html#position" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 70, 173)">position</a></font><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Arial, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="4">() is the selection. If&#160;</font><font face="Arial, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="rgb(103, 41, 103)" size="4"><a href="qtextcursor.html#anchor" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(103, 41, 103)">anchor</a></font><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Arial, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="4">() ==&#160;</font><font face="Arial, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="rgb(0, 70, 173)" size="4"><a href="qtextcursor.html#position" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 70, 173)">position</a></font><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Arial, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="4">() there is no selection. </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      &#30001;&#27492;&#21487;&#35265;&#65292;anchor&#30340;&#20316;&#29992;&#26159;&#22312;&#25991;&#26723;&#20013;&#36873;&#25321;&#25991;&#26412;&#30340;&#26102;&#20505;&#29992;&#26469;&#34920;&#31034;&#36873;&#25321;&#30340;&#36215;&#28857;
    </p>
    <p>
      &#26377;&#19979;&#38754;&#30340;&#25551;&#36848;&#20063;&#21487;&#20197;&#30475;&#20986;&#26469;
    </p>
    <h3 class="fn" style="padding-bottom: 6px; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); font-family: Arial, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; border-left-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; margin-top: 42px; padding-right: 0px; margin-right: 0px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-top-width: 1px; padding-top: 6px; padding-left: 10px">
      int QTextCursor::anchor () const
    </h3>
    <p style="font-family: Arial, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: 4px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-top: 8px">
      Returns the anchor position; this is the same as&#160;<font color="rgb(0, 70, 173)"><a href="qtextcursor.html#position" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 70, 173)">position</a></font>() unless there is a selection in which case&#160;<font color="rgb(0, 70, 173)"><a href="qtextcursor.html#position" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 70, 173)">position</a></font>() marks one end of the selection and anchor() marks the other end. Just like the cursor position, the anchor position is between characters.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family: Arial, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: 4px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-top: 8px">
      QTextCursor&#31867;&#32473;QTextEdit&#31867;&#25552;&#20379;&#20102;&#20809;&#26631;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
